Is that right?

00:47:00.242 --> 00:47:01.700
I was wondering if
you could just--

00:47:01.700 --> 00:47:02.775
HUGH ACHESON: We'll
talk about it.

00:47:02.775 --> 00:47:03.120
Yeah.

00:47:03.120 --> 00:47:04.030
AUDIENCE: Yeah, so I don't know.

